    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sometimes we are pleased that He remains."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We love Him and cherish Him, yet there"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are times that we secretly wish He’d go."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This One, however our Christ we could"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Never escape or evade."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though we would tell Him to just go away"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And to leave us alone,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus won’t leave."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is impossible to be alone."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re single no more; now we are two."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Formerly we were just one by"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ourselves, but now Christ wants to be our life."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Once we got saved we could never again"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be alone by ourselves;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Someone has come, now wherever we go"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And whatever we do,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus is here."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Always this other Person stays with us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He is our life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
